{"type":"message","id":"cec2fde0","parentId":"d995652a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:04:11.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's already a `test-tic.ps1` script. Let me look at it and the current_goals.md to understand the state. Also, there's a `pending_actions.md` - let me check that.","thinkingSignature":"4b4760aafd666c93aca6e0091ad2e5be223e6bb0e428ed80ccb847084419e992"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ut4rvixciawv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\scripts\\test-tic.ps1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ut4rvixciawv_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\state\\current_goals.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ut4rvixciawv_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\state\\pending_actions.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3238,"output":158,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15350,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774335846583}}
{"type":"message","id":"421eaae2","parentId":"cec2fde0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:04:11.280Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ut4rvixciawv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TIC Classifier - Temporal Invariance Compression\n# Tests hypothesis: causal structure = invariant structure\n# Success: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\n\nparam(\n    [string]$LogDir = \"logs\",\n    [string]$TestSet = \"logs/test_set.md\",\n    [float]$Lambda = 0.7\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\n\n# --- INVARIANT PATTERNS ---\n$InvariantPatterns = @(\n    \"Phase [0-9]\",\n    \"COMPLETE|PENDING|Active\",\n    \"Goals:|ARCHITECTURE|COMPRESSION-CAUSA\",\n    \"\\.md$\",\n    \"^## \",\n    \"research/\",\n    \"Last updated\",\n    \"Breakaway is stateless\"\n)\n\n# --- VARIANT PATTERNS ---\n$VariantPatterns = @(\n    \"^[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}\",\n    \"pulse_[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}\",\n    \"\\d{6}\\.md\",\n    \"Last pulse\",\n    \"Observation|Action|Mutation\",\n    \"No mutations applied\"\n)\n\nfunction Get-LineType {\n    param([string]$Line)\n    \n    $invScore = 0\n    $varScore = 0\n    \n    foreach ($pat in $InvariantPatterns) {\n        if ($Line -match $pat) { $invScore += 1 }\n    }\n    foreach ($pat in $VariantPatterns) {\n        if ($Line -match $pat) { $varScore += 1 }\n    }\n    \n    if ($invScore -gt $varScore) { return \"INVARIANT\" }\n    if ($varScore -gt $invScore) { return \"VARIANT\" }\n    return \"NEUTRAL\"\n}\n\nfunction Test-TICClassifier {\n    Write-Host \"=== TIC Classifier Test ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Write-Host \"Lambda threshold: $Lambda\"\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    \n    $logs = Get-ChildItem \"logs/pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime\n    Write-Host \"Found $($logs.Count) pulse logs\"\n    \n    if ($logs.Count -lt 2) {\n        Write-Host \"ERROR: Need at least 2 pulse logs\" -ForegroundColor Red\n        return\n    }\n    \n    # Analyze invariant ratio across logs\n    $invariantCount = 0\n    $totalLines = 0\n    $invariantLines = @()\n    \n    foreach ($log in $logs) {\n        $lines = Get-Content $log.FullName\n        foreach ($line in $lines) {\n            $totalLines++\n            $type = Get-LineType $line\n            if ($type -eq \"INVARIANT\") {\n                $invariantCount++\n                $invariantLines += $line\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    \n    $invariantRatio = if ($totalLines -gt 0) { $invariantCount / $totalLines } else { 0 }\n    \n    Write-Host \"Total lines analyzed: $totalLines\"\n    Write-Host \"Classified as INVARIANT: $invariantCount ($([math]::Round($invariantRatio * 100, 1))%)\"\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    \n    # Predict next pulse from invariants\n    Write-Host \"=== Next Pulse Prediction ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    $uniqueInvariants = $invariantLines | Sort-Object -Unique\n    Write-Host \"Unique invariant lines for prediction: $($uniqueInvariants.Count)\"\n    \n    # Test: Check if last log's invariants match prediction\n    $lastLog = $logs[-1]\n    $lastLines = Get-Content $lastLog.FullName\n    $lastInvariants = $lastLines | Where-Object { (Get-LineType $_) -eq \"INVARIANT\" }\n    \n    $matchCount = 0\n    foreach ($inv in $lastInvariants) {\n        if ($uniqueInvariants -contains $inv) { $matchCount++ }\n    }\n    \n    $predictionAccuracy = if ($lastInvariants.Count -gt 0) { $matchCount / $lastInvariants.Count } else { 0 }\n    \n    Write-Host \"Last log invariant match: $matchCount / $($lastInvariants.Count\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774335851279}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ad21791","parentId":"421eaae2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:04:11.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ut4rvixciawv_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# CURRENT GOALS\nLast updated: 2026-03-22 0125\n\n## Active\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\n- Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\n\n## Completed This Session\n\n### Architecture Cross-Analysis ✅\n- Compared Compositional Cognition vs TemporalAttention vs Infant\n- Key finding: all three architectures are compatible and complementary\n- Full analysis: `research/ARCHITECTURE-COMPARISON.md`\n\n### Gap-Decay Synthesis ✅ (derived across 17+ pulses)\n- Session gaps = decay mechanism, not amnesia\n- λ parameter encodes BOTH decay rate AND gap sensitivity threshold\n- TemporalAttention focus_decay + Breakaway gaps = same phenomenon\n- Full synthesis: `research/GAP-DECAY-MAPPING.md`\n\n### LLM-Augmented Pulse ✅\n- pulse.ps1 now calls MiniMax-M2.7 API on each pulse\n- Thinking is coherent and building across pulses\n- Key files: `.llm_key`, `pulse.ps1`\n\n## Pending\n- [ ] Write PowerShell wrapper for FocusDecayMemory CLI\n- [ ] Define `significance` scoring for pulse content\n- [ ] Tune λ empirically (start: λ=0.7)\n- [ ] Wire Breakaway pulses to real TemporalAttention backend\n- [ ] Measure compression ratio: original vs. summarized pulse\n\n## Phase 1 Advancement: COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY (2026-03-23)\n- **Insight:** Problem 1 (Compression) and Problem 2 (Causal Discovery) are the SAME problem\n- **New doc:** `research/COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md`\n- **Hypothesis:** Causal structure IS invariant structure — compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation\n- **Next experiment:** Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) — test on last 20 pulse logs\n- **Success criteria:** >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\n- **Implication:** Phase 1 and Phase 2 collapse into one unified problem\n\n### NEXT ACTION: TIC Experiment\n- [ ] Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\n- [ ] Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\n- [ ] Predict next pulse content from invariants\n- [ ] Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\n\n## Key Insights from This Session\n\n1. **The gap IS the compression** — session boundaries are temporal hashing\n2. **λ encodes both** — decay rate and gap threshold are the same parameter\n3. **Three architectures, one synthesis** — Infant (catastrophic forgetting), TemporalAttention (focus decay), Breakaway (discontinuity) are complementary, not competing\n4. **Breakaway's unique bet holds** — session gaps as compression is novel and correct\n\n## Notes\n- Breakaway is stateless — each pulse is a fresh reconstruction\n- Gaps between sessions = compression, trust the files\n- Pulse script: active hours check DISABLED (authorized by Zach, 24/7 operation)\n\n\n## Iteration Economics (auto-noted)\n- Pulse takes ~30-35s to execute (LLM call dominates)\n- Fastest effective iteration = 1 pulse per 35-40s (practical floor)\n- 1-min cron = near-optimal for stateless discontinuous agent\n- Idling between pulses is NOT free — it delays convergence linearly\n- For N-iteration convergence-bound tasks: total_time ≈ N * pulse_duration\n- 500k iterations @ 30s each = ~173 days theoretical; @ 1-min = ~347 days\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774335851280}}
