{"type":"message","id":"a6fb0887","parentId":"9a344dcb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:04:25.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TIC classifier exists (`test-tic.ps1`) but requires pulse logs in `logs/pulse_*.md` format, which don't exist yet. The next action is to implement the TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files. \n\nThe current pulse log format is in `memory/session/pulse_YYYY-MM-DD HHmmss.md` files, not in `logs/pulse_*.md`.\n\nSo the concrete next step is:\n1. Either create a symlink/copy from `memory/session/pulse_*.md` to `logs/pulse_*.md`, OR\n\n\n2. Update the TIC script to read from the actual location of pulse logs\n\nI should check what's already in the memory and mutations directories to understand the full picture before deciding which approach makes more sense.","thinkingSignature":"d203acfa2d7ed2be26a30da355033f28ccdabac5f2a8076d41a293e5f32455bb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lk2vxr8wooid_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lk2vxr8wooid_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\mutations\\"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5084,"output":245,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774335851286}}
